Drosophila Melanogaster indexed Transcription starting sites on 2L and 2R chromosomes.

Source: R/baits_Index.gnr.R
baits_Index.gnr.Rd

Data from a CHip Seq experiment

Usage

data(baits_Index.gnr)

Format

An object of class GRanges.

Examples

data(baits_Index.gnr)
